  <brief_title>Study of A Long Lasting Local Anesthestic for Hand, Wrist or Finger Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exparel (Bupivacaine Liposome Injectable Suspension) for Distal Upper Extremity Blocks in Orthopedic Surgery</official_title>
