  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare Exparel, a new, long-lasting numbing medication and a
      shorter-acting nerve block to a traditional single-shot nerve block in patients having hand,
      wrist or finger surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
